    public abstract class AbstractCop1Api<T>
extends Object
implements Api<T>
    the COP1 service is valid for the virtual channel TC links that have useCop1: true the REST interface contains methods for setting/getting the configuration and performing various operations in addition a websocket subscription is available that will allow receiving periodically the status
